-- Constantin Medien Seeks Sports-Unit Investor, Sueddeutsche Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-03-15T18:05:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/constantin-medien-seeks-sports-unit-investor-sueddeutsche-says.html
Constantin Medien AG (EV4)  is looking for
investors for its sports business while aiming to maintain
control over the unit,  Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported, citing
Chief Executive Officer Bernhard Burgener.  The sports business is no longer loss-making, the newspaper
cited Burgener as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
